  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0dd3\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0d9c\u0db8 \u0dc4\u0dbd\u0dd4\u0d9c\u0db8 \u0d9a\u0db1\u0dca\u0daf\u0dda\u0daf\u0dd3 \u0db4\u0dd9\u0da7\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dbd\u0dca \u0db6\u0dc0\u0dd4\u0dc3\u0dbb\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db4\u0dd9\u0dbb\u0dbd\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A petrol bowser overturns at Halugama Hill, Mirigama",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mirigama police say that a bowser carrying a load of petrol has met with an accident at Halugama mountain on the Mirigama Dangowita road this afternoon on the 23rd.",
        "The fuel stock was being transported from Muthurajawela to Peradeniya and the police stated that it contained 33600 liters of petrol.",
        "Preliminary investigations have revealed that the accident occurred when the bowser suddenly ran backwards at the top of Halugama hill.",
        "The police also said that the people who were traveling on the highway at that time collected the petrol that flowed after the bowser overturned."
      ],
